         ROOM A — BALCONY SLABS (ח/C shape)
         West  : X=-8→-3, full N-S (5×16 m)
         South : X=-3→+8, Y=-8→-3 (11×5 m)
         North : X=-3→+8, Y=+3→+8 (11×5 m)
         East side OPEN — no slab facing corridor
         Slab bottom Z=5.0 m; top Z=5.2 m
    ════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

